org.cef.handler

Class CefFocusHandlerAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cef.handler.CefFocusHandlerAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CefFocusHandler 

    public abstract class CefFocusHandlerAdapter
extends java.lang.Object
implements CefFocusHandler
    An abstract adapter class for receiving focus events. The methods in this class are empty. This class exists as convenience for creating handler objects.(用于接收焦点事件的抽象适配器类。此类中的方法为空。此类的存在是为了方便创建处理程序对象。)

                          CefFocusHandler.FocusSource source)
        Description copied from interface: CefFocusHandler
        Called when the browser component is requesting focus.(当浏览器组件请求焦点时调用。)
        Specified by:
        onSetFocus in interface CefFocusHandler

      • onTakeFocus

        public void onTakeFocus(CefBrowser browser,
                        boolean next)
        Description copied from interface: CefFocusHandler
        Called when the browser component is about to loose focus. For instance, if focus was on the last HTML element and the user pressed the TAB key.(当浏览器组件即将失去焦点时调用。例如，如果焦点在最后一个HTML元素上，并且用户按下了TAB键。)
        Specified by:
        onTakeFocus in interface CefFocusHandler
        Parameters:
        browser - The browser generating the event.(browser-生成事件的浏览器。)
        next - will be true if the browser is giving focus to the next component and false if the browser is giving focus to the previous component.(next-如果浏览器将焦点放在下一个组件上，则为true；如果浏览器将重点放在上一个组件，则为false。)
